Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.91,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to be \Nlike this, head in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:26.25,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling to escape from \Nthis saturated world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:32.01,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes like whispering sand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.72,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,These circumstances, unchanging
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.72,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,gazing out at a dreamless tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:45.81,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna say goodbye to the \Nconfusion of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:51.23,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I try reaching out, as if to resist
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:56.95,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,We cry millions of times \Nand then get born again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.16,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with these red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.37,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,to that pictured future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:08.96,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Come here right by me, \NI'm clapping my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.05,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:15.42,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Strain my eyes in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:21.06,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see anything, don't know \Nanything, but I'll still go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:27.39,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,To the place of shining \Nlight in which you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.98,Episode Num,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.98,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.98,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by Ango Sakaguchi's\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Detective Stories)\N"Foolish Apparition" and "The Retard"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:34.74,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,There's no fooling the \NDefeated Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:39.45,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe I'd better call \Nyou the "Great Detective".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.66,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Calls Himself a Novelist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.66,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Prisoner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:41.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.24,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.12,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,A novelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:49.12,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Yuuki Shinjurou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:49.12,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.29,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,I write novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.75,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Not with a pen, but in reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.21,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Great Detective's deductions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:55.09,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,all of the mysteries were to be revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.05,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,and Yajima was supposed \Nto kill his own wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you try to set that up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.22,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's the role \Nof the Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.69,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how cruel the \Nend result will be,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:10.85,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,after all of the victims \Nhave been murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.27,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,the Great Detective wraps everything \Nup with his brilliant deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:16.11,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how tragic the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.57,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,the Great Detective exposes \Nit all to the light of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.37,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,You were {\i1}chosen{\i0} by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.79,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,...to be this world's \Nlast great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.16,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You chose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:32.13,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You're my own \Npersonal great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.00,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:38.05,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry. I'm a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.30,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I know how \Nto do is write stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.05,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Except I don't write \Non manuscript paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.97,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,...but in this reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.56,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If reality becomes a novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.91,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Now go, Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.37,Main Dialog,Novelist,0000,0000,0000,,Unravel the mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The war...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.15,Main Dialog,SFX Director,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.37,Main Dialog,SFX Director,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki-chan, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.50,Main Dialog,SFX Director,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.54,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Over there...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.42,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki-san, the director's \Ncalling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.47,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,What, were you slacking off again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.47,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Izawa Sayo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.47,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:06.10,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,When you have an actress come to \Nfetch you, you must be a big shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.72,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.94,Main Dialog,Tsuneko,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou-kun, we're waiting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.23,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was by the planes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.44,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I called it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.86,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "It \Nfigures", Motoko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:26.03,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,All men love special effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.99,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Even my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.12,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Yada Sumie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.12,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.12,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tanimura Motoko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.12,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.29,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.66,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Motoko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.87,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.08,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,And stop adding "-chan". \NI'm not a little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.21,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka Kichitarou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.21,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Movie Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.63,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.80,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. Okay, should we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Is your makeup all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.68,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:50.35,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not cute, you're not good \Nat your job, Shinjurou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.73,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.02,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me look pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.61,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Director, are we ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,As always, zero enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.04,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just start shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.08,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-san, you must have \Na boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:19.04,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,But Sumie-san, you're more naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.79,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you've never had a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:23.92,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where is this coming from \Nall of a sudden, Motoko-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.26,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to use "chan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.59,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I want to know \Nmore about you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.73,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,We all escaped to here \Nfrom different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.90,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,We were taken in by the owner of \Nthis room and just settled here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:43.36,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,That man treated us equally, l... l...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.49,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,Loving us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.82,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.82,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, he disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.66,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,...and now we just loiter \Nin this burning town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.25,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,But I hear the director hasn't \Ndecided on the last scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:01.67,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows if we can be \Nreunited with the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.55,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the four of us can live \Nhappily together again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.26,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.26,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to choose one of \Nus from the three, like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.05,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:13.31,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.73,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.85,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,They really do look happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.94,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.31,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Solve the mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:04.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.57,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.82,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot... Red...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.66,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.54,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna die... We're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.30,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.94,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But why do I have to \N"solve the mystery"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:51.45,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,when a crime or whatever \Nhasn't even happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:55.62,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,If a war really did happen, I don't \Nthink there would be any escaping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.08,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.87,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.45,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've never even imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:04.54,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know what to do if I looked \Nout the window and saw a bomb dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:10.05,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... The last war was before \Nmy grandpa's time, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.05,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,A war isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.09,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,No one is losing their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.76,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Houses aren't burning down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.97,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,No one is grieving...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.14,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why we can make \Na movie about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.41,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, can we do a retake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.20,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.78,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Because Sayo-san showed me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.45,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I can do better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.75,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Director, I have a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.54,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.12,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you standing around chatting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.38,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Director, can we do it one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:52.17,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,You know that I'm the \Ndirector, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.92,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.68,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Director, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.81,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If we can do it for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.10,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.48,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?! I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:10.77,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.98,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.24,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.30,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.01,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I need to \Ntalk to the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,This movie has a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Something isn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.98,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't \Nyou? You're Papillon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.03,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.11,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.20,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.78,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.78,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.95,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just do what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.37,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, right here, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.85,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Yuuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:23.76,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.73,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing, Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.14,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I've been entrusted with a movie camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,For days now, I've been \Non location for a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:47.45,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The silly premise is that modern-day \NJapan has become embroiled in a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Was the director with \None of the actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.47,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mystery here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The mystery will be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The truth must be revealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There was... no war...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.38,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,JJ... Systems...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.52,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mamori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,"Mamori"... "Kaze"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.27,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.52,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.42,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.04,Main Dialog,Director,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,About last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.51,Main Dialog,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mitaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.30,Main Dialog,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenberg and Schaffner, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:23.84,Main Dialog,Director,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.31,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Works of Director Frank Darabont
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.93,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a mystery too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.57,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Each is responding \Ncompletely differently...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.41,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what the director wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.87,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.25,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I found shade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:01.92,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou, are you \Nlooking at women again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.68,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you mean the actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.76,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tanimura, Yada are \Nthere... and Izawa, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.35,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:32.91,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki-san! Actually, we wanted to ask \Nthe director something about the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:37.37,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,So we said to him, "We know \Nthe script isn't finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.50,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,but are we going somewhere?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:44.05,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,And he said, "You can't go \Nanywhere. You're criminals."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.55,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you think \Ntoo, Shinjurou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.80,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know who we are \Nor where we've come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.60,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,and we can't even go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.85,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,There is this line...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.48,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,War is a toy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.19,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.27,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, too. And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.94,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,We've all made war into a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.70,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,We should've sucked off war more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:11.37,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,We should've wrapped our legs around \Nwar and ridden it until it was worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:14.66,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sucked it more, get more \Ntangled up with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:19.50,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the lines we say when \Nwe hear that the war's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:25.13,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,We all have different interpretations \Nof what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:31.01,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm thinking it means we're \Nhappy that the war is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.18,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,so now we can get back \Nto our normal lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:37.94,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,But it made me so curious that I wanted \Nto ask the director what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.35,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.69,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,"Normal lives" has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.82,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's more like there's a \Nwar and we're just running around,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:49.15,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,but meanwhile maybe we finally \Nrealize that we're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:55.24,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,We've become just like beasts \Nwho only think of survival...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:59.12,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,But there's still the one who's \Nprecious to us, whom we l-l...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.08,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.25,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.42,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand it, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:08.05,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's that feeling, like you want \Nto try living on the edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.88,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Where you get sick of the tedious \Ndays that never change...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.35,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my take on it \Nis a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:18.89,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I think it means that we're all going \Nto be put on trial by the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.60,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Put on trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:24.48,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Good people, bad people, they \Nall die the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:28.44,Main Dialog,Sumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's what he meant when \Nhe said we were "criminals".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.53,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You're all over thinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.16,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,This is a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.66,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Shinjurou-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.16,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,If you're right, then why bother \Nmaking a movie like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:41.17,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of this nonexistent \Nwar, what are we running for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.92,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,We're running because \Nof our everyday lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.09,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Because we've realized how \Nprecious those ordinary,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.42,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,run-of-the-mill days are to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.21,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.72,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is secretly wishing for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.68,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not for a war, but for \Nsomething big to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.72,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will \Nchange what we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:59.22,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Something that'll let us \Nfind what's really precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:05.31,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,But think of people who lose their family \Nor home in a volcanic eruption or fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.73,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,They wish they could have their \Neveryday life back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.32,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,But there are people who go to \Na volcano or fire just to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.03,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we know just \Nhow sad it would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:21.50,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,we have this desire to mess up \Nthe world... and ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:25.50,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,So I think it means that \Nhas to be put on trial...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:32.26,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I see... The mystery that is a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.97,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.01,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,You have been listening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.26,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of us do you think is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:44.27,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I'll ask the director \Nabout the ending and try writing it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll find some \Nkind of answer that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.94,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.28,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, lunch break's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.20,Main Dialog,Three,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.12,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,But Motoko, this is..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.42,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.34,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.42,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that was one of the three...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.49,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,...they're embracing life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.61,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,They're betting on the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.93,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Director! What's this about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.10,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to ruin the whole thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.64,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,What have you got there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.26,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.02,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.52,Main Dialog,Motoko,0000,0000,0000,,The director is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:55.48,Main Dialog,Sumie,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he was run \Nover by the streetcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.28,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That's just part of the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.11,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The streetcar's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:04.16,Main Dialog,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It seems no one saw Mr. \NMitaka after lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:08.83,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm the last one who talked to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.50,Main Dialog,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,But why was he killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.42,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Only one person has a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The person who was angry at Director \NMitaka, who was going to wreck the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:22.05,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and all the hard work \Nthese women put into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.60,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.73,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.31,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.94,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you dreaming about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:39.45,Main Dialog,Mitaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's all made-up! A lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.11,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.68,Main Dialog,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki-san, stop it! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.73,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's telling me \Nto solve the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If I gather clues and \Ndeduce the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.95,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only possible culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.16,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,That's a confession, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.12,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Kaishou Rie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.12,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Metropolitan Police Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.30,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kaishou, with the \NMetro Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:43.26,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest for the murder \Nof movie director Mitaka Kichitarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:07.16,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,In the pale morning \Nmist, a whispered prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:15.12,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna follow this \Ntwisted landscape with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:23.17,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for the "truth", \N"a 'lie' will do" is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:31.56,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tracing it as if we can see through
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:35.48,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, beyond words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:39.48,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a falling feather
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.48,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:47.91,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:07.34,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, unravel it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:11.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tattered cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:14.31,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:19.52,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:27.40,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to let me \Nsee Shinjurou! All right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:33.45,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Inga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:33.45,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Detective's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:33.99,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:43.09,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I smell her here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.93,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hayami Seigen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.93,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Director of the Security Bureau \NMetropolitan Police Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:55.47,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's all the screen \Ntime I get?! What's the idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:58.27,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what'll happen \Nif you make me angry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:23:02.69,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Look, part of the next episode was \Ninspired by "The Election Murder Case",
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:06.49,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,and if you read the story first, \Nit gives you all kinds of spoilers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:08.03,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Should I spill? Should I talk? \NShould I give the game away here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:08.99,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:10.41,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, K-K-Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.78,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! O-Okay! I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.79,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on UN-GO: \N"The King of Paradise".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:18.96,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, Kazamori!!
